# Portfolio architecture

## Structure

- Single-page app: `src/App.jsx` composes sections in order
- Section HOC: `src/hoc/SectionWrapper.jsx` — Framer `whileInView`, hash `id` for nav
- Mobile: `SkillsSimple` when viewport ≤ 768px; else `Skills`

## Data

- Static content: `src/constants/index.js` (nav, services, experiences, projects, testimonials)
- Live GitHub: `src/utils/github.js` — used by `GitHubStats.jsx` only unless user approves Works integration
- Resume generators: `src/utils/resume.js`

## 3D

- Hero uses `ComputersCanvas` (lazy-loaded from `src/components/canvas/`)
- GLTF assets live in `public/desktop_pc/` and `public/planet/` — use root `public/` only (not `src/public/`)

## Routing

- `BrowserRouter` for logo link only; navigation is hash-based (`#about`, `#skills`, etc.)

## Build

- Vite `base: "/My_Portfolio/"` for GitHub Pages
